title: Study of a coach
description: Sketch of a carosse-coupe.(?) At left the front of the coach with a small front wheel and above a cushion for a coachman to sit.  At the center a slight trapezoidal shaped body of the coach with a front window and throughout simple edge ornamentation.  A large wheel at the rear of the coach.
name: Drawing
